headline: Brock Purdy and "Tractor Kid" Jackson Team Up with John Deere to Fuel Farmers and Fight Hunger
summary: What happens when a pro quarterback and a 10-year-old tractor expert try to cook a meal for America's farmers? Spoiler: they're better off in the field than in the kitchen—just watch the chaos unfold.
